name: Hell Raiser OG
awards: 1st place in concentrates category at the 2014 High Times San Francisco Cannabis Cup
description: Hell Raiser OG is a 60% indica-dominant hybrid bred by Archive Seed Bank. The strain is a cross of two beloved OGs: Fire OG and Face Off OG. After its 72-day flowering time indoors, Hell Raiser OG produces round, crystal covered buds that show off its OG lineage through a sour lemon and pine aroma. Hell Raiser OG took 1st place in the concentrates category at the 2014 High Times San Francisco Cannabis Cup.
